overview: WAKE UP - LIFE - REPEAT  Everyone doing the same thing everyday, this monotone life may get a little heavy once in a while. But there is no time and place to take a break from it. This is why vacation should be like a daily suplement. Something we could take once every morning, like a vitamin.
tagline: Vitamin, Sea, Stress, Life, Depression, Vacation, Monotone
title: Vitamin Sea
